{"tid":1566714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［中秋求安慰］自從6月我同班港豬廢青朋友絕左交⋯","createTime":"2019-09-13T17:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T17:41:49.000Z","uid":260501,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8afcb8220506a3daa0ef852f623a4043bcc7581d","tid":1566714,"uid":260501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"我地係青梅竹馬，612個日見佢地post吃喝玩樂嘅相，佢地咁多次遊行只係去過2佰萬個一次<br />\n<br />\n今日中秋⋯我自己一個行上獅子山<br />\n我知道佢哋又去咗玩好開心<br />\n到12點幾落山，向大圍方向行<br />\n<br />\n沿途落山既一個人都無<br />\n電筒又玩到無左電<br />\n突然間漆黑一片，我大喊左出黎⋯<br />\n之後開着手機燈，聽住國歌<br />\n我先有勇氣跑落去<br />\n<br />\n落到去終於見到有人落山，<br />\n有啲人企埋一邊同我地講加油<br />\n我又忍唔住喊咗出嚟<br />\n<br />\n另一半又係外國，<br />\n我而家最好嘅朋友係我屋企隻狗<br />\n<br />\n突然間今年中秋對我好大打擊⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n冇錯 我係呢段期間係識左啲手足<br />\n但係大時大節佢哋都有佢哋嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n我個心真係好痛，好放唔低⋯⋯"},{"pid":"05fe2ab178aaa8ecbbe314df22b6c702e315645c","tid":1566714,"uid":260501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec3b774e8d0139afe5f0189871087ad190f97460","tid":1566714,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"你有冇去約手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />足"},{"pid":"476cc1016e08d7d98160fd5e459b93a6172ad33e","tid":1566714,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n915見"},{"pid":"604c7522731e23283618fda235340f9b8fb37b0a","tid":1566714,"uid":260501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec3b774e8d0139afe5f0189871087ad190f97460","tid":1566714,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"你有冇去約手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:09:10.000Z","msg":"佢地唔上獅子山，有d就同自己fd..."},{"pid":"697b9c4b7cd6838fa20ada4a05185ebfe7a5aec0","tid":1566714,"uid":260501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"476cc1016e08d7d98160fd5e459b93